    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you look at the environmental side though, there's a lot of data about how much it actually helps with carbon levels and air quality. From an urban planning perspective, is there a strong consensus on whether these programs are actually effective at meeting climate goals, or is that also part of the debate?",
